reviews.review_text: 1st Love This was my 4th show & where I met my first Love. I had hitch hiked down to Miami to do the Fla tour & record. The sound on this recording is good for an audience. It sounds like I was plugged into the same mics. I had my masters stollen not long afterwards & was only able to find a copy of the second set. The whole show rocked. A Long first set with Highlights including The Roses, On The Road Again, The Race Is On. Second set opened with a smoking Cold Rain & Snow & then surprise Encore of Satisfaction.

Love this little run This is the first of four shows thru the Southeast.  All four are worth listening to.  The best is 11/29, but this is sweet too.  The audience recording makes it even better.  Try the auds for all 4.
